com.snakybo.torch.input.keyboard

Enum Key

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Key>
      • com.snakybo.torch.input.keyboard.Key
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Key>

    public enum Key
extends java.lang.Enum<Key>

    All available keyboard buttons.

    This is a direct implementation of the GLFW keys.

    1.0
